    "Lessons learned from the incident are used to amend the recovery plan and processes, aligning them with security goals and objectives.",
    "AI can play a role in automatically reviewing existing strategies, incident reports, and audit logs to identify opportunities for improvement based on the latest breach, thus informing future response planning.• Analysis and aggregation of incident reports-The analysis and aggregation of security incident data and reports provide valuable insights that can guide advancements in cybersecurity.",
    "However, managing and analyzing incident data can be a challenging and time-consuming task.",
    "AI techniques can be applied to efficiently collect, aggregate, extract information, visualize data, and predict patterns in heterogeneous incident data.",
    "As an illustration, Meyers and Meneely pioneered an innovative automated approach that leverages the power of natural language processing to scrutinize vulnerabilities and unveil intricate connections among them."
